HEADWORD: Frue vanner
<hw>Frue" van"ner</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Etymol. uncertain.]</ety>
<fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>A moving, inclined, endless apron on which ore
is concentrated by a current of water; a kind of buddle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frugal</ent>⟦br⟧
